high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter to the left of the white stove.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the white table on the right.
Slice the head of lettuce on the table.
Turn left, take a right and walk to the black fridge on the left.
Put the knife inside the fridge on the bottom shelf and close the door.
Turn left, hang a left at the counter and walk to the white table on the left.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the table.
Turn left, take a right and walk to the black fridge on the left.
Put the slice of lettuce on the top shelf inside the fridge, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the slice of chilled lettuce inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill a knife and place a chilled slice of lettuce in a sink.
